Oluwaseun Ayodeji Osowobi bụ onye Naijiria na-ahụ maka ihe ndị ruuru ụmụ nwaanyi
O bu onye guzobere Stand to End Rape (STER) Mmalite
N'afọ 2019 ọ bụ nwaanyi Naijiria nke abụọ a kpọrọ aha na Time 100 Next list, ọ bụkwa onye ntorobia Commonwealth n'afo ahu.

A mụrụ Osowobi ma zụlite ya na Naijiria, ebe nne ya kpaliri ya ịghọ onye nkwado. O nwetara nzere bachelọ na gọọmentị ime obodo na ọmụmụ mmepe na Mahadum Ahmadu Bello tupu ọ banye na Mahadum Swansea maka nzere masta na International Relations
Thesis ya lekwasịrị anya na nha nhata nwoke na nwanyị na mpụ mmekọahụ megide ụmụ nwanyị na ụmụaka.
N'oge ọ na-arụ ọrụ na National Youth Service, Osowobi rụrụ ọrụ maka Independent National Electoral Commission na ntuli aka 2011
Mgbe ọ na-arụ ọrụ, o kwuru, "ndị obodo na ndị obodo..
setịpụrụ ọnyà maka (ya) ka otu n'ime ụmụ nwoke obodo ahụ dinaa ya n'ike" mgbe ọ jụrụ iri ngo

Mgbe nke ahụ gasịrị, o guzobere Stand to End Rape (STER) na 2013. Omume a na-achọ imeziwanye mmata banyere ime ihe ike megide ụmụ nwaanyi  n'inye nkwado maka ndị a wakporo. Site n'afọ 2019, oge mere atụmatụ na nzukọ ahụ eruola ihe dị ka ndị Naijiria Puku nari naira abuo.
Osowobi nwetara onyinye Genius Grant site na John D

MacArthur Foundation na 2017. N'afọ 2019, a kpọrọ ya aha dị ka otu n'ime ndị Time 100 Next nke afọ, bụrụ nwaanyi Naijiria nke abụọ mere ndepụta ahụ. A kpọkwara ya onye ntorobịa Commonwealth nke Afọ 2019.
